data.description: Spacious & Sunny 5-Bedroom Family Home at 11909 Asbury Dr, Fort Washington, MD  Welcome to 11909 Asbury Dr, Fort Washington, MD, a single-family residence that combines comfort and convenience in the heart of Maryland. This lovely 1-story home, covering an expansive area of 1,492 sqft, is ready and awaiting its new owners.  The property features five sizable bedrooms and two well-appointed bathrooms. The highlight being the master bedroom and living room include natural light flooding in through the large windows, enhancing the warmth of the wooden flooring.  A standout feature of this property includes the south-facing windows, ensuring a naturally lit living experience year-round. Complete with an attached garage with two spaces, this home offers both functionality and convenience.    Extra amenities include two sizable lower-level guest rooms and a basement offering additional storage or potential living space.  Located near the top-rated Friendly High School and Oxon Hill Middle School, this home is ideal for families. The neighborhood not only provides street parking and nearby public transportation but is also within proximity of the lush Fort Washington Park, Fort Foote Park, Tantallon North Neighborhood Park, and the serene Potomac Landing Park.  Don't miss out on owning this comfortable and inviting house. Embark on your hassle-free living journey at 11909 Asbury Drive, Fort Washington MD. The home is a blank canvas in a great location with enormous potential.  Contact us today to arrange a viewing.
